items.name: XYZprinting da Vinci Duo 2.0 3D Printer
items.shortDescription: Unleash your inner creativity with the XYZ Da Vinci 3D Printer. It features two extruders, allowing you to create multicolor projects using the 13 filament colors available in easy-to-install cartridges. Watch through the transparent case as the object you dreamed up in your mind becomes a solid thing you can hold in your hands. Use this da Vinci printer to build toys, prototypes, models or whatever else you care to invent. Its Fused Filament Fabrication technology allows it to use 1.75mm filament to construct three-dimensional objects at your command. This XYZ 3D printer supports Windows operating systems after XP as well as Mac OSX 10.8 and above for added versatility. It has USB 2.0 connectivity for fast data transfer. Join XYZprinting's global 3D design community, 3D Design Hub and Artist Collection to create, share and download hundreds of designs from all over the world.
